criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged 18 to 60 years old, male or female;

          -  Conform to the diagnostic criteria of immune Thrombocytopenia (ITP)

          -  Needed splenectomy;

          -  People who are willing to sign the informed consent voluntarily and follow the
             research program.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Secondary thrombocytopenic purpura;

          -  Patients with poor compliance;

          -  Researchers believe that patients should not participate in the test of any other
             condition.
